    "en": {
      "title": "Rule of law must be upheld: Juli Sangh",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The US ambassador to Sri Lanka, Julie Singh, said that the rule of law should be established.",
        "He also noted that a peaceful transfer of power is necessary within Sri Lanka's democratic and constitutional framework.",
        "According to this, the people's demands for accountability, transparency, democratic governance and a better future can be fulfilled, said Julie Sung, the US Ambassador to Sri Lanka. (a)"
      ],
